        <h1>
Implement a CORBA client and server
(Python recipe)
<span class="print_only secondary">by Duncan Grisby</span>

<div class="print_only secondary" style="margin-top: 10px;">
  ActiveState Code (http://code.activestate.com/recipes/81254/)
</div>
</h1>
      </div>
      

      <div id="content">
        
