<td>

  <div id="description">
  <p>CORBA has a reputation for being hard to use, but it is really very easy, expecially if you use Python. This example shows the complete implementation of a fortune cookie server and its client.</p>

  </div>
  
  <div id="blocks">
  
    <div id="block-0" class="block">
    
      <div class="block-toolbar as_secondary">
